-  [Sync, EnableIf=is_win]
+  // texture; |rect| is its window-relative device-pixel placement. Replies with
+  // the woven output, or null if the weave failed / the session isn't live.
+  //
+  // ASYNC (was [Sync] through B4d): a synchronous mojo call from the GPU process
+  // is banned (sync_call_restrictions — the browser may sync-wait on the GPU
